From,their,site,Allows,access,to,all,of,the,arXiv,data,search,and,linking,facilities,The,Cornell,University,e,print,arXiv,hosted,at,arXiv,org,is,a,document,submission,and,retrieval,system,used,by,the,physics,mathematics,and,computer,science,communities,It,has,become,the,primary,means,of,communicating,manuscripts,on,current,and,ongoing,research,The,arXiv,repository,is,available,worldwide,Manuscripts,are,often,submitted,to,the,arXiv,before,they,are,published,by,more,traditional,means,In,some,cases,they,may,never,be,submitted,or,published,elsewhere,The,purpose,of,the,arXiv,API,is,to,allow,programmatic,access,to,the,arXiv,s,e,print,content,and,metadata,The,goal,of,the,interface,is,to,facilitate,new,use,of,the,the,vast,body,of,material,on,the,arXiv